text: <!channel> Hello team Compass! Since we’re all WHF’ing today, I thought we could have stanup over slack!!

There isn’t anything on compass-dev Trello for this iteration, so I’m planning to try my best to get caught up on what Israel’s done recently over Slack...

Over break I wrote scenarios for Daniel and am tightening those up today, as well as writing some for Courtney. I’ve also summarized the worksession that Matt/Ewald/I had and added some relevant slides to my Personas keynote. I’ve shared that as WIP with Katrina but am going to continue generating questions and checking that work against the feature set that was born out of the first set of scenarios.
Try to fix my laptop. Because of the weather might not be able to get in and get a loaner.
I've started on BLE code in the Android app, but there's not much more to do on BLE until we have the prototype wearable and can start testing and thinking about how connection logic will work.

I have concepts that Israel and I talked about working on. The concept of “Places” and how we can architect it is the top on my list. Not sure when I’ll be getting to that today as I really need to finish a feature for live case.

I'm gonna keep pushing/researching/sketching. Had a handful of new ideas over the break, and want to see where they go. Either way, I'll need to start putting more concrete shape to abstract ideas so we can talk about them as a group.
Working on getting Megan Hansen ramped into the mix, working with design team to figure out what next steps should be (touching base throughout day)
